text: Charles Vanderbyl (5 April 1874 - 9 February 1956) was a British fencer. He competed in the individual sabre and épée events at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1874 births Category:1956 deaths Category:British male fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Great Britain Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Paddington Category:Sportspeople from London
